NETS 4 ;
    - b/net2 ( b/leaf A ) ( b/leaf_2 Z ) + USE SIGNAL
      + ROUTED metal3 ( 190 1260 ) ( 5890 * )
      NEW metal1 ( 190 1260 ) via1_4
      NEW metal2 ( 190 1260 ) via2_5
      NEW metal1 ( 5890 1260 ) via1_4
      NEW metal2 ( 5890 1260 ) via2_5 ;
    - mid ( leaf ZN ) + USE SIGNAL ;
    - w0 ( load0 A ) ( leaf A ) ( b/leaf ZN ) + USE SIGNAL
